Clearways are strict no-parking zones and apply even to local residents or Mobility Scheme Permit holders. Check signs before parking as vehicles left in clearways will be towed and a fee applies.

properties.otherAdvice:
Rolling road closures will be in place from approx 12pm until 1pm on sections of Young St, Bent St, Bligh St and Castlereagh St in the Sydney CBD for a Police Operation. Roads will progressively re-open when safe to do so.

Motorists travelling in the city should use Elizabeth St while Castlereagh St is closed. 

Expect delays and follow the directions of NSW Police on site.
